entry.title: C A A MOBILE PHONE SPARE PARTS L.L.C
entry.content:
Company Profile

As an international mobile accessories supplier headquartered in Dubai, Caa has become one of the most influential companies in the Middle East region since our establishment in 2009. We stand out with outstanding service, high-quality products, and competitive prices.

In China, Caa operates our own manufacturing facility, enabling independent development, research, and production to ensure strict control over product quality. Our products are highly regarded in the market and are exported to countries across Africa, the Middle East, Europe, and Southeast Asia.

Caa offers a wide range of mobile accessories, including LCD screens, touch screens, batteries, charging Port Board, and power Button Flex, compatible with popular brands such as Tecno,Infinix,Itel, Iphone, Samsung, Nokia, Huawei, Honor, Xiaomi, Vivo, Oppo, Realme, Alcatel, Lenovo, and Google. Partnering with Caa, you can expect exceptional service, premium-quality products, and competitive prices.

We are committed to providing the best solutions for your mobile accessory needs. We look forward to collaborating with you!
